 -- Steven Ayre <steveayre@gmail.com>  Mon, 25 Jun 2012 22:03:33 +0100

mysql-cluster-7.2 (7.2.6-0.1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New upstream version
  * Add package mysql-common-cluster
    * Depends on mysql-common (mysql-5.5) for my.cnf, adds
      cluster-specific options in /etc/mysql/conf.d/my-cluster.cnf
  * Add package mysql-client-core-cluster-7.2
  * Add package mysql-cluster-clusterj
  * Packaging updates
    * Changed to 3.0 (quilt) format
    * Add ccache DEB_BUILD_OPTIONS option
    * Move from dh_movefiles to dh_install
    * Move manpage files from .files to .manpages
    * Move some files between packages to avoid conflicting with
    * Merged some changes from mysql-5.5 source package
    * Re-enabled libmysqlclient18 versioned symbols check
      Missing symbols were fixed upstream - libndbclient6 still lacking.
    * Updated debian/watch

 -- Steven Ayre <steveayre@gmail.com>  Mon, 25 Jun 2012 16:27:35 +0100

