mysql-cluster-7.2 (7.2.5-0.4) stable; urgency=low

  * Updated mysql init.d script
      * Added START_DAEMON option in defaults file (default is true)
      * Added STARTUP_WAIT_FOREVER option in defaults (default is false),
        on start init.d script waits for mysql to be ready or stop running

